rComments: It was an okay class overall. Starts out really easy but turns out to be super hard nearing the end. The final exam was really difficult. If you like business and graphs and word problems alot though, I guess its ok.

For a math class, he made going pretty fun. When I came early he would always have some type of slide up to talk about with the class. He's very approachable. Homework was always due before class started, so if you are always late it could be problematic (as in you receive a zero on it). I was disappointed that he didn't teach AMS11B
